2,537 likes, 41 comments - danwintersphoto on April 30, 2024: "Willie Nelson, Bakersfield, CA.  Fun fact:  Willie Nelson was born in Abbott, Texas in 1933.  He was born just before midnight on April 29th, but back then the county courthouse registered late night births the next day.  So his birth certificate reads April 30th.  He celebrates his Birthday on both days.  Youâ€™re welcome.  Happy Birthday Willie!@willienelsonofficial.  91 years on this earth is a long time.  A national treasure if there ever was one. @willienelsonofficial
#willienelson #nationaltreasure".
